**Functions:**

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [register](file:///D:/Major/backend/controllers/authController.mjs#8-104) | Hash password, generate & email OTP, save user |
| [verifyOtp](file:///D:/Major/backend/controllers/authController.mjs#105-156) | Verify OTP, issue JWT, mark user verified |
