| [resetPasswordWithOtp](file:///D:/Major/backend/controllers/authController.mjs#311-363) | Verify OTP, hash new password, save |

Imports: `bcrypt`, `jwt`, `User` model, [generateOTP](file:///D:/Major/backend/utils/generateOTP.mjs#3-9), [sendMail](file:///D:/Major/backend/utils/emailNotifier.mjs#25-62), `getTranslation`

