| [getNearbyDonors](file:///D:/Major/backend/controllers/donorsController.mjs#46-107) | MongoDB `$geoNear` aggregation to find donors within radius |

**Geo-matching logic:**
```javascript
User.aggregate([
  { $geoNear: {
      near: { type: "Point", coordinates: [lng, lat] },
      distanceField: "dist.calculated",
      query: { available: true },
      spherical: true,
      maxDistance: 20000  // 20km default
  }},
  { $limit: 6 }
])
```

