### [controllers/requestController.mjs](file:///D:/Major/backend/controllers/requestController.mjs) — Blood Request Lifecycle
The largest controller (~59KB). Manages complete request lifecycle:

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `createRequest` | Create new blood request, geocode location, notify donors |
| `getRecentRequests` | Fetch open/recent requests for dashboard |
| `claimRequest` | Donor claims request (becomes primary) |
| `registerInterest` | Donor sends interest (becomes backup), triggers email offer |
| `confirmInterest` | Donor clicks YES/NO in email → updates Offer status |
| `watchRequest` | Donor in cooldown adds themselves as watcher |
| `verifyArrival` | Donor confirms arrival at hospital |
| `completeDonation` | Mark donation done, award Hero Coins |
| `cancelDonation` | Donor cancels, next backup promoted |
| `closeRequest` | Requester closes fulfilled request |
| `verifyDonation` | Verify donation slip/confirmation |
| `getMyRequests` | Fetch requests created by logged-in user |
| `getMyDonations` | Fetch donations made by logged-in user |

