### [controllers/notifyController.mjs](file:///D:/Major/backend/controllers/notifyController.mjs) — Notification Engine
Central hub for **targeted donor notifications**:
- Finds eligible donors by blood group compatibility + geography
- Sends personalised donation offer emails with branded HTML templates
- Handles `Offer` model — tracks each donor's YES/NO response with secure token
- Manages offer response (email click → server updates offer → promotes donor)
- Sends follow-up confirmations, donor-assigned alerts, requester notifications

