Provides analytics data for the Analytics page:
- Aggregates donation statistics, blood group distribution, request trends
- Integrates with Python ML models (calls [backend/ai/main.py](file:///D:/Major/backend/ai/main.py) subprocess)
- Returns data for: Donor Readiness Score, Blood Shortage Risk, 7-Day Demand Simulation

