### [utils/scheduler.mjs](file:///D:/Major/backend/utils/scheduler.mjs) — Background Job Runner
Called [initScheduler()](file:///D:/Major/backend/utils/scheduler.mjs#16-32) from [server.mjs](file:///D:/Major/backend/server.mjs). Runs every **5 minutes**:

| Job | Logic |
|---|---|
| [checkTimeouts()](file:///D:/Major/backend/utils/scheduler.mjs#33-56) | Finds primary donors who accepted >2 hours ago but haven't arrived → promotes backup or re-opens request |
| [cleanupOldRequests()](file:///D:/Major/backend/utils/scheduler.mjs#135-147) | Deletes requests older than 7 days |
| [checkWatchers()](file:///D:/Major/backend/utils/scheduler.mjs#148-200) | Finds open requests >6 hours old with un-notified watchers → sends re-engagement email |
| [selfPing()](file:///D:/Major/backend/utils/scheduler.mjs#7-15) | Pings `SERVER_BASE` URL to prevent Render free-tier sleep |

