### [middleware/authMiddleware.mjs](file:///D:/Major/backend/middleware/authMiddleware.mjs) — JWT Auth Guard
```javascript
// Extracts Bearer token from Authorization header
// jwt.verify(token, JWT_SECRET) → decoded { id, email }
// User.findById(decoded.id) → attaches req.user
// Returns 401 if token invalid/expired
```

