## 4. Frontend Modules

All pages are in `frontend/src/pages/`. Uses React Router v7 for routing.

| Page | Route | API Calls | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| `Home.js` | `/` | `/api/requests/recent` | Landing, shows open requests map & stats |
| `Login.js` | `/login` | `POST /api/auth/login` | Email+password login, stores JWT |
| `Register.js` | `/register` | `POST /api/auth/register` | Registration form, triggers OTP flow |
| `VerifyOtp.js` | `/verify-otp` | `POST /api/auth/verify-otp`, `POST /api/auth/resend-otp` | OTP entry with countdown timer |
| `Forgot.js` | `/forgot` | `POST /api/auth/forgot-password-otp`, `POST /api/auth/reset-password-otp` | Password reset flow |
| `Dashboard.js` | `/dashboard` | `/api/user/me`, `/api/requests/recent` | Main donor dashboard |
| `Donate.js` | `/donate` | `/api/donors/nearby`, `/api/requests/*` | Find requests, offer to donate |
| `Request.js` | `/request` | `POST /api/requests/create` | Post a new blood request |
| `Donations.js` | `/donations` | `/api/requests/my-donations` | User's donation history |
| `RequestedDonations.js` | `/my-requests` | `/api/requests/my-requests` | User's posted requests |
| `Profile.js` | `/profile` | `/api/user/me`, `PUT /api/user/update` | Edit profile, upload photo |
| `Analytics.js` | `/analytics` | `/api/analytics/*` | Charts, ML model outputs |
| `Gamification.js` | `/gamification` | `/api/rewards/*` | Hero Coins, badges, levels |
| `Leaderboard.js` | `/leaderboard` | `/api/rewards/leaderboard` | Top donors ranking |
| `Rewards.js` | `/rewards` | `/api/redeem/*` | Redeem coins for offers |
| `MediBotPage.js` | `/medibot` | `POST /api/medibot/chat` | AI chatbot interface |
| `MapPage.js` | `/map` | `/api/donors/nearby` | Map of nearby donors |
| `LanguageSettings.js` | `/language` | `PUT /api/user/update` | User language preference |
| `Splash.js` | `/splash` | — | Loading/splash screen |

**Components:**
- `Sidebar.js` — Navigation sidebar with links
- `MapComponent.js` — Leaflet.js map with donor/request pins
- `Filters/` — Blood group, urgency, distance filter components
- `MediBot/` — Chat UI for the AI bot

**Data Flow Pattern (example: Register → OTP):**
```
User types email/password → Register.js state
↓ Submit → axios.post("/api/auth/register", { name, email, password })
↓ 201 OK received → navigate to /verify-otp?email=...
↓ VerifyOtp.js → user enters 6-digit code
↓ axios.post("/api/auth/verify-otp", { email, otp })
↓ 200 OK + JWT token received → stored in localStorage
↓ navigate to /dashboard
```

