## 6. Database Design

MongoDB Atlas, accessed via **Mongoose ODM**.

### Collection: `users`

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `uid` | String | Unique internal ID (`local-<timestamp>`) |
| `email` | String | Unique, required |
| `password` | String | bcrypt hashed |
| `name` | String | |
| `isVerified` | Boolean | Set true after OTP verified |
| `otp` | String | bcrypt-hashed OTP (null after verification) |
| `otpExpires` | Date | 10-minute TTL |
| `otpAttempts` | Number | Max 5 before lockout |
| `lastOtpSent` | Date | Cooldown reference |
| `blood` / `bloodGroup` | String | e.g., "A+" |
| `available` | Boolean | Donor availability toggle |
| `location` | `{lat, lng}` | Simple lat/lng |
| `locationGeo` | GeoJSON Point | `{type:"Point", coordinates:[lng,lat]}` |
| `lastDonation` | Date | For cooldown calculation |
| `donationsCount` | Number | Lifetime donation count |
| `heroCoins` / `coins` | Number | Gamification currency |
| `leaderboardPoints` | Number | Rank on leaderboard |
| `reliabilityScore` | Number | 0–100, default 100 |
| `badges` | [String] | Achievement badges |
| `preferredLanguage` | String | For i18n emails |
| `profilePhoto` | String | Base64 encoded image |

**Indexes:** `locationGeo: "2dsphere"` (geospatial), `leaderboardPoints: -1`

---

### Collection: `requests`

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `name` | String | Patient/requester name |
| `bloodGroup` | String | Required |
| `hospital` | String | Required |
| `phone` | String | Contact number |
| `units` | Number | Units of blood needed |
| `urgency` | Enum | `low/normal/high/critical` |
| `status` | Enum | `open/primary_assigned/backup_assigned/pending_verification/fulfilled/failed/cancelled` |
| `locationGeo` | GeoJSON | For geo-matching |
| `primaryDonor` | Object | `{donorId, acceptedAt, confirmedAt, arrived}` |
| `backupDonors` | Array | List of backup donor objects |
| `watchers` | Array | `{donorId, email, name, notified}` |
| `expiresAt` | Date | Auto-set to +7 days |

**Index:** `locationGeo: "2dsphere"`

---

### Collection: `offers`

Tracks each donor's email-based response to a donation request:

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `donorUserId` | ObjectId → User | |
| `requestId` | ObjectId → Request | Required |
| `token` | String | Unique secure token for email links |
| `response` | Enum | `yes/no/null` |
| `status` | Enum | `pending/accepted/declined` |
| `followUpAt` | Date | When to send follow-up |
| `coinsAwarded` | Boolean | Prevent double rewarding |

---

### Collection: `notifications`
`{userId, title, body, meta, createdAt}`

### Collection: `chatSessions`
`{userId, messages:[{role, content}], createdAt}`

### Collection: `gamifications`
`{userId, coins, badges, level}`

### Collection: `rewardlogs`
`{userId, action, coins, description, createdAt}`

### Collection: `redemptions`
`{userId, optionId, coinsSpent, status, createdAt}`

